General.Name: Nickel X Limited
General.Description: NickelX Limited, a mining exploration company, focuses on exploring nickel deposits in Western Australia. The company also explores for copper, cobalt, and gold. Its flagship project is the Biranup project covering an area of 342 square kilometers located in the Albany Fraser Orogen, Western Australia. The company was formerly known as New Energy Metals Limited. NickelX Limited was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Perth, Australia.
